        <Parent_String>Italic terra sigillata [300301418], terra sigillata ware [300387395], pottery by kiln, location, or style [300387412], pottery (visual works) [300010666], ceramic ware (visual works) [300386879], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
